formula.text: KPI("Undesired Activities", VARIABLE(<%= CASE_TABLE %>), VARIABLE(<%= process %>), VARIABLE(<%= language %>), VARIABLE(<%= Undesired %>))
KPI("Undesired Activity Rate", VARIABLE(<%= process %>), VARIABLE(<%= language %>), VARIABLE(<%= Undesired %>))

meta.expressionLhs: CASE WHEN MONTH ( "EKKO"."AEDAT" ) >= 10 THEN YEAR ( "EKKO"."AEDAT" ) || '-' || MONTH ( "EKKO"."AEDAT" ) ELSE YEAR ( "EKKO"."AEDAT" ) || '-0' || MONTH ( "EKKO"."AEDAT" ) END AS "Timeframe" FORMAT "%Y-%m"

components.title: Trend - <%= CASE_ITEM %>s with Undesired Activities by <%=TIMEFRAME_TEXT%>

meta.expressionLhs: CASE WHEN PU_COUNT ( "EKPO" , "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN" , "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN" IN ( 'Block Purchase Order Item' , 'Cancel Goods Receipt' , 'Change Currency' , 'Change Price' , 'Change Quantity' , 'Delete Purchase Order Item' , 'Dun Order Confirmation' , 'Refuse Purchase Order Item' ) ) > 0 THEN 'PO item with undesired activity' ELSE 'clean PO item' END AS "Unwanted"

axis0.name: Unwanted
axis0.text:
CASE 
    WHEN PU_COUNT("<%= CASE_TABLE %>","_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>","_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" IN (<%=Undesired%>)) > 0 
    THEN '<%= CASE_ITEM %> with undesired activity' 
    ELSE  'clean <%= CASE_ITEM %>' 
END

axis0.name: #{activity}
axis0.text: CASE WHEN "_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>"  IN (<%=Undesired%>) THEN "_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" ELSE NULL END

axis2.name: # <%= CASE_ITEM %>s with Undesired Activities
axis2.text:
COUNT(DISTINCT 
 
CASE WHEN PU_COUNT("<%= CASE_TABLE %>","_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>","_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" IN (<%=Undesired%>)) > 0 
           AND "_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>"  IN (<%=Undesired%>) 
THEN "_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."_CASE_KEY" ELSE NULL END
 
)

axis2.name: Undesired Activity Rate
axis2.text:
COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN "_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" IN (<%=Undesired%>) THEN "_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."_CASE_KEY" ELSE NULL END)
/
COUNT(DISTINCT "_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."_CASE_KEY")

axis2.name: UAR only manual execution
axis2.text:
COUNT(DISTINCT 
 
CASE WHEN PU_COUNT("<%= CASE_TABLE %>","_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>","_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" IN (<%=Undesired%>)) > 0 
           AND "_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>"  IN (<%=Undesired%>)
                  AND  "_CEL_<%=process%>_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE" IN (<%=auto_user_type%>)
THEN "_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."_CASE_KEY" ELSE NULL END
 
)

axis2.name: # Undesired Activities
axis2.text: SUM(CASE WHEN "_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>"  IN (<%=Undesired%>) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)

axis2.name: # <%= CASE_ITEM %>s with Undesired Activities
axis2.text:
COUNT(DISTINCT 
 
CASE WHEN PU_COUNT("<%= CASE_TABLE %>","_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>","_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" IN (<%=Undesired%>)) > 0 
           AND "_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>"  IN (<%=Undesired%>) 
THEN "_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."_CASE_KEY" ELSE NULL END
 
)

/
COUNT(DISTINCT "_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."_CASE_KEY")

variables.title: TIMEFRAME
variables.variableValue:
CASE
WHEN MONTH("EKKO"."AEDAT") IN (10,11,12) THEN YEAR("EKKO"."AEDAT") || ' - Q1'
WHEN MONTH("EKKO"."AEDAT") IN (1,2,3) THEN YEAR("EKKO"."AEDAT") || ' - Q2'
WHEN MONTH("EKKO"."AEDAT") IN (4,5,6) THEN YEAR("EKKO"."AEDAT" ) || ' - Q3'
WHEN MONTH("EKKO"."AEDAT") IN (7,8,9) THEN YEAR("EKKO"."AEDAT") || ' - Q4'
ELSE NULL
END

variables.title: TIMEFRAME
variables.variableValue:
CASE -- 2 digit Month
WHEN MONTH("EKKO"."AEDAT") >= 10
THEN YEAR("EKKO"."AEDAT") ||'-' || MONTH("EKKO"."AEDAT")
ELSE YEAR("EKKO"."AEDAT") ||'-0' || MONTH("EKKO"."AEDAT")
END

variables.title: TIMEFRAME
variables.variableValue:
CASE
WHEN CALENDAR_WEEK("EKKO"."AEDAT") >= 10
THEN YEAR("EKKO"."AEDAT")
--- ADD one Year if we are already in CW 1 at the end of December
+ CASE WHEN MONTH("EKKO"."AEDAT") = 12 AND CALENDAR_WEEK("EKKO"."AEDAT") = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END
|| '-CW-' ||CALENDAR_WEEK("EKKO"."AEDAT")
ELSE YEAR("EKKO"."AEDAT") || '-CW-0' ||CALENDAR_WEEK("EKKO"."AEDAT")
END

variables.title: TIMEFRAME
variables.variableValue:
CASE -- 2 digit Month
WHEN MONTH( "EKKO"."AEDAT" ) >= 10
THEN CASE
WHEN DAY("EKKO"."AEDAT" ) >= 10
THEN YEAR("EKKO"."AEDAT" ) ||'-'|| MONTH("EKKO"."AEDAT" ) ||'-' || DAY("EKKO"."AEDAT" )
ELSE YEAR("EKKO"."AEDAT" ) ||'-'|| MONTH("EKKO"."AEDAT" ) ||'-0' || DAY("EKKO"."AEDAT" )
END
ELSE CASE
WHEN DAY("EKKO"."AEDAT" ) >= 10
THEN YEAR("EKKO"."AEDAT" ) ||'-0'|| MONTH("EKKO"."AEDAT" ) ||'-' || DAY("EKKO"."AEDAT" )
ELSE YEAR("EKKO"."AEDAT" ) ||'-0'|| MONTH("EKKO"."AEDAT" ) ||'-0' || DAY("EKKO"."AEDAT" )
END
END
